data.description: This home is truly one of a kind and a designer's DREAM! Located in the highly sought Westgate subdivision, zoned to CFISD. This home has NO CARPET throughout the entire house. Gorgeous remodel of kitchen and living area including Faux Concrete Countertops and newly installed Backsplash and Light Fixtures. Every detail has been meticulously thought through. You will not want to miss this home! Large backyard, great for family BBQ's and entertaining. Call today to schedule your appointment!
